Command.Name: echoCommand
Command.Description: Echos back whatever is input to the command, used to verify the command system is working correctly.

Command.Name: version
Command.Description: Displays the current version of the application.

Command.Name: about
Command.Description: Displays the about message for the current application.

Command.Name: name
Command.Description: Displays a message with the name of the current application

Command.Name: commandSequencer
Command.Description: Takes a sequence of commands and/or command aliases and enqueues all of those commands into the command queue.

Command.Name: workflow
Command.Description: Loads the specified workflow from the D-data structure and calls the command sequencer to get each of the commands in the workflow into the command queue.

Command.Name: commandGenerator
Command.Description: Generates a series of commands given an input command pattern and enqueues them to the command queue for execution
